@startuml
title BR Check-In - Activity Diagram

start

:Request Check-In;
note right
Student initiates check-in from the Check-in UI.
end note

:Display Progress;
note right
System shows check-in progress or processing status to the student.
end note

:Send Check-In Request;
note right
Check-in UI sends checkIn(bookingId) to CheckInController.
end note

:Validate Active Booking;
note right
CheckInController verifies whether the booking is active using Booking.
end note

if (Booking Active?) then (Yes)
  :Mark Room Occupied;
  note right
  System updates the Room status to occupied.
  end note

  :Record Check-In Log;
  note right
  System records check-in details
  (studentId, roomId, time) in CheckInLog.
  end note

  :Return Check-In Status (Success);
  note right
  CheckInController returns successful check-in status
  to the Check-in UI.
  end note
else (No)
  :Return Check-In Status (Failure);
  note right
  System returns failed check-in status for invalid
  or inactive booking.
  end note
endif

:Show Check-In Confirmation;
note right
Check-in UI displays confirmation or an error message to the student.
end note

stop
@enduml
